{"article_id":"bNFvN0lGy1AbyeM3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"HONG KONG","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Hong Kong leader Carrie Lam on Wednesday withdrew an extradition bill","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"that triggered months of often violent protests","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"so the Chinese-ruled city can move forward from a \" highly vulnerable and dangerous \" place","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and find solutions .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"Her televised announcement came","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"after reports on Friday and Monday revealing","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"Beijing thwarted an earlier proposal from Lam","depth":14},{"id":9,"text":"to withdraw the bill","depth":14},{"id":10,"text":"and she had said privately","depth":14},{"id":11,"text":"that she would resign","depth":15},{"id":12,"text":"if she could .","depth":15},{"id":13,"text":"\" Lingering violence is damaging the very foundations of our society , especially the rule of law , \"","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"a sombre Lam said","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"as she sat wearing a navy blue jacket and pink shirt","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"with her hands folded on a desk .","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"It was not clear when the recording was made .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"The withdrawal needs the approval of the Legislative Council ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"which is not expected to oppose Lam .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The bill would have allowed extraditions to mainland China","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"where courts are controlled by the Communist Party .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Its withdrawal is a key demand of protesters but just one of five .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The move came after pitched battles across the former British colony of 7 million .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"More than 1,000 protesters were arrested .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Many are furious about perceived police brutality and the number of arrests","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and want an independent inquiry .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" The government will formally withdraw the bill","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"in order to fully allay public concerns , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Lam said .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"\" I pledge","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that the government will seriously follow up the recommendations of the IPCC","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"( Independent Police Complaints Council )","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"report .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"From this month , I and my principal officials will reach out to the community","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"to start a direct dialogue ...","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"we must find ways","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"to address the discontent in society","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"and look for solutions . \"","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"The protests began in March","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"but snowballed in June","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and have evolved into a push for greater democracy for the city","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"which returned to China in 1997 .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"It was not clear","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"if killing the bill would help end the unrest .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"The immediate reaction appeared sceptical .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"\" The damage has been done .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"The scars and wounds are still bleeding , \"","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"said pro-democracy legislator Claudia Mo .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" She thinks","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"she can use a garden hose","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to put out a hill fire .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"That ' s not going to be acceptable . \"","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Many people on street corners after nightfall were shouting :","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"\" Five demands ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"not one missing . \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"\" We still have four other demands .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"We hope","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"people won ' t forget that , \"","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"said a woman","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"speaking for the protest movement","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"who declined to identify herself except by the surname Chan .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"\" The mobilisation power won ' t decrease . \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Riot police fired beanbag guns and used pepper spray on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to clear demonstrators from outside the Mong Kok police station and in Prince Edward metro station ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"with one man taken out on a stretcher with an oxygen mask over his face ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"television footage showed .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"The four other demands are :","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"retraction of the word \" riot \"","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"to describe rallies , release of all demonstrators , an independent inquiry into perceived police brutality and the right","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"for Hong Kong people","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"to choose their own leaders .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"\" Too little , too late , \"","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"Joshua Wong , a leader of pro-democracy protests in 2014","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"that were the precursor to the current unrest ,","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"said on his Facebook page .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"In the United States , Republican Senator Marco Rubio ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"a persistent critic of what he sees as Beijing ' s attempts","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"to undermine Hong Kong ' s autonomy ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"called Lam ' s move \" welcome but insufficient . \"","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"\" The Chinese Communist Party should uphold its commitments to Hong Kong ' s autonomy","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and stop aggravating the situation with threats of violence , \"","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"U.S. Democratic House speaker Nancy Pelosi called the move long overdue","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"and demanded an end to the use of force against demonstrators .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"she looked forward to the swift advance of bipartisan legislation","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"to reaffirm the U.S. commitment to democracy , human rights and the rule of law in Hong Kong .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Riot police officers stand guard at Po Lam Mass Transit Railway","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"( MTR )","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"station , during an anti-extradition bill protest in Hong Kong , China","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"September 5 , 2019 .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"/Tyrone Siu","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Rubio has co-sponsored a Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that would require annual certification of Hong Kong ' s autonomy","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"to justify special treatment","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"the territory enjoys under U.S. law .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"In an op-ed in the Washington Post on Tuesday , Rubio said","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"the United States and the rest of the world needed to make clear to China","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"that aggression towards Hong Kong risked \" swift , severe and lasting consequences . \"","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"the U.S. administration should make clear","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"it could respond \" flexibly and robustly , \"","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"including with sanctions against the police force and individuals responsible for abuses .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"The U.S. State Department did not immediately respond to a request for comment .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"In a voice recording","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"obtained by ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Lam said at a meeting last week","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"that her room","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"to find a political solution to the crisis","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"was \" very limited \" ,","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"as authorities in Beijing now viewed the situation as a matter of national security .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"The protests are the biggest popular challenge to Chinese President Xi Jinping ' s rule","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"since he took power in 2012 .","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"Beijing denies meddling in Hong Kong ' s affairs ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"yet it warned again on Tuesday","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"that it would act","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"if protests threatened Chinese security and sovereignty .","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"Pro-Beijing lawmaker Cheung Kwok-kwan said","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"Lam ' s announcement was not a compromise","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"to appease those promoting violence","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"but a bid","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"to win over moderates in the protest camp .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"\" It was likely speaking to the so-called peaceful , rational , non-violent people","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"who were dissatisfied with the government ' s response before , \"","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"The chief executive ' s office did not immediately respond to a request for comment on the bill ' s withdrawal .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Hong Kong 's benchmark Hang Seng Index .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"HSI jumped after the report of the bill 's imminent withdrawal ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"trading up about 4 % .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"The property index also jumped .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Hong Kong returned to China under a \" one country , two systems \" formula","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"that allowed it to keep freedoms","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"not enjoyed on the mainland , like the freedom","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"to protest and an independent legal system ,","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"hence the anger at the extradition bill and perceived creeping influence by Beijing .","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"Beijing has regularly warned about the impact on Hong Kong ' s economy .","depth":5},{"id":137,"text":"Cathay Pacific Airways","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"( 0293.HK )","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"has been one of the biggest corporate casualties .","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"China ' s aviation regulator demanded","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"Cathay suspend staff from flying over its airspace","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"if they were involved in , or supported , the demonstrations","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"and the airline has laid off at least 20 personnel , including pilots and cabin crew .","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"On Wednesday it announced the resignation of chairman John Slosar","depth":4},{"id":145,"text":"following the departure of CEO Rupert Hogg last month .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":0,"right":290,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":290,"left":275,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":1,"right":274,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":274,"left":219,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":182,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":165,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":163,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":161,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":149,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint",